reviewText: My kindergarten and first grade students love to watch and draw with Pappy!
Loved this show when I was a kid and now my daughter loves it. Worth every penny!!!!
The DVD was as described and was quickly delivered. Thank you!
Second generation of pappyland artists in our house
I have been waiting a long time for pappyland on DVD and it will soon finally be here.  Pappy is good with the kids and teaches them manners and how to draw
